<item>
            <title>[LU-15936] DOSTID macro is not printing llog IDs properly in the logs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15936</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;DOSTID&lt;/tt&gt; macro is not printing the FID of llog files properly in the logs.  It is printing logids like &quot;&lt;tt&gt;0x2:2147506325:0&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; but the FID is actually &quot;&lt;tt&gt;0x1280005895:0x2:0x0&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, which makes debugging llog problems difficult.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;DOSTID&lt;/tt&gt; macro should be fixed to print the llog FIDs properly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
