                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="337564" author="adilger" created="Sun, 12 Jun 2022 02:28:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This &lt;tt&gt;DOSTID&lt;/tt&gt; formatting problem was likely introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9153&quot; title=&quot;improve FID/config name specification for lctl llog_print and llog_info&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9153&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9153&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; trying to transition the FID printing between the old format and the new format.  At this point it is very unlikely that anything is using the old format and it should just always print the llog IDs as proper FIDs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
